---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout 
  title="Root Canal Therapy" 
  category="General Dentistry"
  description="Save your natural tooth with advanced root canal treatment. Modern techniques make this procedure comfortable and effective."
  image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1579684385127-1ef15d508118?w=1920&h=600&fit=crop"
>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-accent-100 to-accent-200/50 border-l-4 border-accent-300 p-6 rounded-r-lg mb-8">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-2">Save Your Natural Tooth</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-0">
        Root canal therapy allows us to save teeth that would otherwise need extraction. Using modern 
        techniques and anesthesia, we make the procedure comfortable while preserving your natural smile.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      When is Root Canal Therapy Needed?
    </h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <!-- Signs & Symptoms -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Signs You May Need Treatment</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7 4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-9a1 1 0 00-1 1v4a1 1 0 102 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Severe tooth pain when chewing or applying pressure</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7 4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-9a1 1 0 00-1 1v4a1 1 0 102 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Prolonged sensitivity to hot or cold temperatures</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7 4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-9a1 1 0 00-1 1v4a1 1 0 102 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Darkening or discoloration of the tooth</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7 4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-9a1 1 0 00-1 1v4a1 1 0 102 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Swelling and tenderness in nearby gums</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7 4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zm-1-9a1 1 0 00-1 1v4a1 1 0 102 0V6a1 1 0 00-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Recurring pimple on the gums</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Benefits -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-primary-100/30 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">Benefits of Root Canal Therapy</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Saves your natural tooth</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Eliminates infection and pain</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Prevents spread of infection</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>Maintains natural bite and chewing</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            <span>More affordable than extraction and replacement</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      The Root Canal Process
    </h2>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-50 to-accent-100/30 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-900 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">1</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Diagnosis & Preparation</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            X-rays confirm the infection. Local anesthetic ensures you're comfortable throughout the procedure.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-900 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">2</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Cleaning & Shaping</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Infected pulp is removed, canals are cleaned, shaped, and disinfected to eliminate bacteria.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-900 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">3</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold mb-2">Filling & Sealing</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            Canals are filled with biocompatible material and sealed. A crown is usually placed for protection.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-semibold text-dental-charcoal mb-6">
      Modern Technology for Comfort
    </h2>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Digital X-Rays</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          High-resolution imaging for precise diagnosis with 90% less radiation than traditional X-rays.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-6">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-900" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Rotary Instruments</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          Electric handpieces provide more efficient cleaning with less vibration and noise for patient comfort.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-primary-900 text-white rounded-2xl p-8">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading font-semibold mb-4">
        Don't Let Tooth Pain Control Your Life
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Modern root canal therapy is comfortable and effective. We'll save your natural tooth 
        and eliminate your pain, often in just one appointment.
      </p>
      <a href="#book-appointment" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent-300 text-primary-900 px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
        Schedule Your Consultation
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Related Services -->
  <div slot="related-services" class="space-y-3">
    <a href="/services/crowns-bridges" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Dental Crowns</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Protect tooth after root canal</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/emergency-dental" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Emergency Dental Care</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Same-day pain relief</p>
    </a>
    <a href="/services/fillings" class="block p-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-dental-charcoal">Dental Fillings</h4>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Treat cavities early</p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div slot="faq" class="space-y-6">
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">Is root canal therapy painful?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Modern root canal therapy is no more uncomfortable than getting a filling. We use local anesthetic 
        to ensure you're completely numb during the procedure. Most patients report that the relief from 
        their tooth pain makes the procedure worthwhile.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How many appointments will I need?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Most root canals can be completed in one or two appointments. The number of visits depends on 
        the complexity of your case and whether there's an active infection. We'll give you a clear 
        treatment timeline during your consultation.
      </p>
    </details>
    
    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">What happens after root canal therapy?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        After the root canal, your tooth will need a permanent restoration, usually a crown, to protect 
        it from fracture. You may experience mild soreness for a few days, which can be managed with 
        over-the-counter pain medication.
      </p>
    </details>

    <details class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
      <summary class="font-semibold text-lg cursor-pointer">How successful is root canal therapy?</summary>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        Root canal therapy has a success rate of over 95%. With proper care and regular dental visits, 
        a tooth that has had a root canal can last a lifetime. The key is completing the treatment with 
        a proper restoration like a crown.
      </p>
    </details>
  </div>

</ServiceLayout>